{"title":"char数组转list","date":"2019-03-10T22:52:25.000Z","link":"post/320","categories":["Java"],"updated":"2019-04-26T14:58:52.681Z","content":"<h3 id=\"方法1\">方法1<a href=\"post/320#方法1\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">myString.chars().mapToObj(c -&gt; (<span class=\"keyword\">char</span>) c).collect(Collectors.toList());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"方法2\">方法2<a href=\"post/320#方法2\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">String s = <span class=\"string\">\"asdasdasda\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">char</span>[] chars = s.toCharArray();</span><br><span class=\"line\">List&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">char</span>[]&gt; asList = Arrays.asList(chars);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    List&lt;Character&gt; listC = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ArrayList&lt;Character&gt;();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">char</span> c : chars) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        listC.add(c);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","prev":{"title":"you are not allowed to push code to protected branches on this project","link":"post/322"},"next":{"title":"java获取当前月和下个月的第一天和最后一天","link":"post/318"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/320/"}